      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, representing a premier choice for the discerning driver. This unit exhibits a robust mechanical profile and a well-preserved interior, ensuring a sophisticated driving experience. Meticulously serviced and ready for immediate delivery, this automobile offers an exceptional balance of performance and long-term value.",
      "price": 36850.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
